{
  "texts": [
    "In 2021, following the idea of the transformer, Tan et al.",
    "proposed RTD-Net, which is similar to the transformer architecture.",
    "There are three main improvements to DETR.",
    "To solve the problem of slow video processing, an attentive boundary module is used to replace the encoder in the transformer.",
    "In order to adapt to the problems of blurred time boundaries and sparse annotation and to reduce the single, strict evaluation criteria from the ground-truth, the relatively relaxed matching scheme is proposed."
  ]
}